        <div class="skill-box">PyArrow</div>
        <div class="skill-box">asyncio</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="skills-category">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-slate-200 mb-2">Tools & Platforms</h3>
      <div class="skills-container">
        <div class="skill-box">Docker</div>
        <div class="skill-box">Git</div>
        <div class="skill-box">AWS</div>
        <div class="skill-box">Linux</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold section-header-title">Related Publications</div>
    <hr class="section-header-hr">
  </div>
  <div class="mb-10 publication-container">
    <ul class="space-y-3">
      <li><a href="https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00466-025-02691-5"><strong>Revising the Structure of Recurrent Neural Networks to Eliminate Numerical Derivatives in Physics-Informed Loss Terms with Respect to Time Computational Mechanics (2025).</strong></a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-024-74711-y"><strong>Enhancing convergence speed with feature enforcing physics-informed neural networks using boundary conditions as prior knowledge., Scientific Reports (2024)</strong></a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold section-header-title">Education</div>
    <hr class="section-header-hr">
  </div>
  <div class="timeline-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ph.D. in Artificial Intelligence and Data Science"
      subtitle="2025 – Present | Monash University, Melbourne, Australia"
    >
      Thesis: Building and enhancing AI agents through Neuro-Symbolic and physics-informed machine learning.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="M.Sc. in Scientific Machine Learning"
      subtitle="2024 | Sharif University of Technology, Tehran, Iran"
    >
      Research-based Master's focused on the mutual application of computer science and engineering principles.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="B.Sc. in Engineering"
      subtitle="2022 | Imam Khomeini International University, Qazvin, Iran"
    >
      Specialization in Robotics.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  :root {
    --primary-color: #000000; /* Light Blue */
    --secondary-color: #2dd4bf; /* Teal */
    --background-color: #030000; /* Slate-800 */
    --card-color: #909aaa; /* Slate-700 */
    --border-color: #000000; /* Slate-600 */
    --text-color: #000000; /* Slate-300 */
    --heading-color: #000000; /* Slate-100 */
  }

  /* --- Section Header Styling --- */
  .section-header-title {
    color: var(--heading-color);
  }
  .section-header-hr {
    border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);
    width: 50px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* --- Timeline Visualization --- */
  .timeline-container {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 30px; /* Space for the timeline line and dots */
  }

  .timeline-container::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 10px;
    bottom: 10px;
    width: 2px;
    background-color: var(--border-color);
  }

  .timeline-element::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -30px; 
    top: 10px; 
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
    border: 2px solid var(--background-color);
    z-index: 10;
  }
  .timeline-element {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-left: 15px; 
    color: var(--text-color);
  }
  .timeline-element h3 { color: var(--heading-color); }
  .timeline-element h4 { color: var(--text-color); opacity: 0.8; }

  /* --- Skills Section --- */
  .skills-category {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .skills-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .skill-box {
    background-color: var(--card-color);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    color: var(--text-color);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
  }
  .skill-box:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
    color: var(--background-color);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.2);
  }

  /* --- Publications Section --- */
  .publication-container a {
    color: var(--text-color);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .publication-container a:hover {
    color: var(--secondary-color);
  }
  .publication-container a strong {
    color: var(--heading-color);
  }
</style>
